'''卡尔曼综合征'''（{{lang-en|Kallmann syndrome}}）是一种罕见的[[遺傳性疾病|遺傳性疾病]]，其特点是患者无法进入[[青春期|青春期]]或青春期发育不完全。该疾病也伴随嗅觉丧失或嗅觉减退。此种疾病男女皆可发病，但多见于男性。患者若不进行治疗大多会出现[[不孕|不育]]的情况。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Digenic mutations account for variable phenotypes in idiopathic hypogonadotropic hypogonadism|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC1765517/|last=Pitteloud|first=Nelly|last2=Quinton|first2=Richard|date=2007-02-01|journal=Journal of Clinical Investigation|issue=2|doi=10.1172/JCI29884|volume=117|pages=457–463|issn=0021-9738|pmc=1765517|pmid=17235395|last3=Pearce|first3=Simon|last4=Raivio|first4=Taneli|last5=Acierno|first5=James|last6=Dwyer|first6=Andrew|last7=Plummer|first7=Lacey|last8=Hughes|first8=Virginia|last9=Seminara|first9=Stephanie}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Kallmann syndrome: adhesion, afferents, and anosmia|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12062015|last=MacColl|first=Gavin|last2=Bouloux|first2=Pierre|date=2002-05-30|journal=Neuron|issue=5|volume=34|pages=675–678|issn=0896-6273|pmid=12062015|last3=Quinton|first3=Richard|access-date=2016-08-08|archive-date=2018-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180706104006/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12062015|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://gene.hpa.gov.tw/index.php?mo=DiseasePaper&action=paper1_show&cate=Set1&csn=69&sn=296&print=true|title=衛生福利部國民健康署遺傳疾病諮詢服務窗口|accessdate=2016-08-08|work=gene.hpa.gov.tw|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919022209/https://gene.hpa.gov.tw/index.php?mo=DiseasePaper&action=paper1_show&cate=Set1&csn=69&sn=296&print=true|archive-date=2016-09-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

卡尔曼综合征的产生是由于在胚胎發育过程中，[[促性腺激素释放激素|促性腺激素释放激素]]释放神经元无法迁移到正确的位置，导致[[下丘脑|下丘脑]]无法在适当的时间释放促性腺激素释放激素。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Luteinizing hormone-releasing hormone (LHRH)-expressing cells do not migrate normally in an inherited hypogonadal (Kallmann) syndrome|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/2687610|last=Schwanzel-Fukuda|first=M.|last2=Bick|first2=D.|date=1989-12-01|journal=Brain Research. Molecular Brain Research|issue=4|volume=6|pages=311–326|issn=0169-328X|pmid=2687610|last3=Pfaff|first3=D. W.|access-date=2016-08-08|archive-date=2019-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190607164831/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/2687610|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Reproduction, smell, and neurodevelopmental disorders: genetic defects in different hypogonadotropic hypogonadal syndromes|url=http://journal.frontiersin.org/article/10.3389/fendo.2014.00109/abstract|last=Valdes-Socin|first=Hernan|last2=Rubio Almanza|first2=Matilde|date=2014-01-01|journal=Neuroendocrine Science|doi=10.3389/fendo.2014.00109|volume=5|pages=109|pmc=4088923|pmid=25071724|last3=Tomé Fernández-Ladreda|first3=Mariana|last4=Debray|first4=François Guillaume|last5=Bours|first5=Vincent|last6=Beckers|first6=Albert|access-date=2016-08-08|archive-date=2016-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405200954/http://journal.frontiersin.org/article/10.3389/fendo.2014.00109/abstract|dead-url=no}}</ref>

卡尔曼综合征是[[性腺机能减退|性腺机能减退]]的一种形式。在出现性腺机能减退且伴随嗅觉丧失的人群中约有50％被列为卡尔曼综合征。除去嗅觉丧失的症状，针对卡尔曼综合征和性腺机能减退的诊疗并没有什么区别。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Expert consensus document: European Consensus Statement on congenital hypogonadotropic hypogonadism--pathogenesis, diagnosis and treatment|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/26194704|last=Boehm|first=Ulrich|last2=Bouloux|first2=Pierre-Marc|date=2015-09-01|journal=Nature Reviews. Endocrinology|issue=9|doi=10.1038/nrendo.2015.112|volume=11|pages=547–564|issn=1759-5037|pmid=26194704|last3=Dattani|first3=Mehul T.|last4=de Roux|first4=Nicolas|last5=Dodé|first5=Catherine|last6=Dunkel|first6=Leo|last7=Dwyer|first7=Andrew A.|last8=Giacobini|first8=Paolo|last9=Hardelin|first9=Jean-Pierre|access-date=2016-08-08|archive-date=2019-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604083828/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/26194704|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Treatment of isolated hypogonadotropic hypogonadism effect on bone mineral density and bone turnover|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9024272|last=Guo|first=C. Y.|last2=Jones|first2=T. H.|date=1997-02-01|journal=The Journal of Clinical Endocrinology and Metabolism|issue=2|doi=10.1210/jcem.82.2.3758|volume=82|pages=658–665|issn=0021-972X|pmid=9024272|last3=Eastell|first3=R.|access-date=2016-08-08|archive-date=2019-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604194327/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9024272|dead-url=no}}</ref>

此病由德裔美籍[[精神科醫師|精神科醫師]][[法蘭茲·約瑟夫·卡爾曼|法蘭茲·約瑟夫·卡爾曼]]（Franz Josef Kallmann）於1944年首次描述，因此以他的姓氏命名。

